<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Portfolio</title>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background: #0077b6;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
        }

        header img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 4px solid white;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        nav {
            background: #023e8a;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: yellow;
        }

        section {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #0077b6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        .project {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        form input,
        form textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        form button {
            background: #0077b6;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        form button:hover {
            background: #023e8a;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            background: #023e8a;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Your Name</h1>
        <img src="profile.jpg" alt="Profile Picture">
        <p>
            Hello! I am a passionate student interested in web development,
            programming, and learning new technologies.
        </p>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#education">Education</a>
        <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
        <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>
            I am a motivated learner with an interest in creating websites and
            software applications. I enjoy solving problems and continuously
            improving my technical skills.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section id="education">
        <h2>Education</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Bachelor of Computer Applications (BCA) - XYZ College</li>
            <li>Higher Secondary - ABC School</li>
            <li>Secondary School - ABC School</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="skills">
        <h2>Skills</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>HTML</li>
            <li>CSS</li>
            <li>JavaScript</li>
            <li>C Programming</li>
            <li>Python</li>
            <li>MS Office</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="projects">
        <h2>Projects</h2>

        <div class="project">
            <h3>Personal Portfolio Website</h3>
            <p>
                Designed a responsive portfolio website using HTML and CSS.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="project">
            <h3>Student Management System</h3>
            <p>
                Developed a basic student record management application.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
        <h2>Contact Me</h2>

        <form>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required>

            <input type="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>

            <textarea rows="5" placeholder="Your Message"></textarea>

            <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
        </form>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Your Name | All Rights Reserved</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
